e limits $L\\to0^+$, $L\\to +\\infty$, $s\\to0^+$ and $s\\to 1^-$ are also\nexplored, and we find interesting connections with well-studied diffusion\nproblems. Finally, we propose convergent monotone finite-difference schemes and\ninclude numerical experiments aimed at illustrating some of the obtained\ntheoretical results, as well as other interesting phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Nov 2019 00:08:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 21:22:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2022 12:40:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-22"}
